<section>
  <title>gentoo-dev</title>
  <body>

  <p><b>Grading Portage updates.</b></p>
  <p>We all love portage for the ease with which it means we can all keep up-to-date systems, but have you just wanted to do critical updates, without having to recompile {X, KDE, GNOME} in the process? Well that was the suggestion made <uri link="http://marc.theaimsgroup.com/?l=gentoo-dev&amp;m=107815541006048&amp;w=2">here</uri>.</p>

  </body>
</section>

